All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChanceRow
    ChanceRow extends ScoreRow for the "Chance" category and implements the ChanceRow.isValid(Dice) function.
    Dice
    Class to define an array of die
    Die
    Class to define a single die
    FixedAmountRow
    FixedAmountRow is an abstraction of ScoreRow that implements the score calculations in FixedAmountRow.calculateScore(Dice) for all its sub-classes.
    FullHouseRow
    FullHouseRow extends ScoreRow for the "Full House" category and implements the FullHouseRow.isValid(Dice) function.
    NumberRow
    NumberRow extends ScoreRow for the "Ones", "Twos", ...
    NumOfAKindRow
    NumberRow extends ScoreRow for the "Three and Four of a Kind" categories and implements the NumOfAKindRow.isValid(Dice) function.
    ScoreRow
    ScoreRow represents one scoring row of the ScoreSheet.
    ScoreSheet
    List of ScoreRow that contains are the scoring categories and their scores.
    StraightRow
    StraightRow extends ScoreRow for the "Small Straight" and "Large Straight" categories and implements the StraightRow.isValid(Dice) function.
    SumAllRow
    SumAllRow is an abstraction of ScoreRow that generalizes the score calculations in SumAllRow.calculateScore(Dice).
    Yahtzee
    Class to play the game of Yahtzee and test the isValid method of the score rows
    YahtzeeRow
    NumberRow extends ScoreRow for the "Yahtzee" category and implements the isValid(Dice) function.
